Package: BCDAG
Title: Bayesian Structure and Causal Learning of Gaussian Directed
        Graphs
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Federico",
           family = "Castelletti",
           role = "aut",
           email = "federico.castelletti@unicatt.it"),
           person(given = "Alessandro",
           family = "Mascaro",
